p.span: A genetically modified autologous CD34+ cell enriched population that contains haematopoietic stem cells transduced with lentiviral vector encoding the A-T87Q-globin gene with a strength of 1.220 106 cell/mL.
Also contains Cryostor CS5 and sodium chloride.
See Lot Information Sheet for number of infusion bags and CD34+ cells per kg for this patient.
Read the package leaflet before use.

title.value: 6. SPECIAL WARNING THAT THE MEDICINAL PRODUCT MUST BE STORED OUT OF THE SIGHT AND REACH OF CHILDREN

p.span: Keep out of the sight and reach of children.
Store in the vapour phase of liquid nitrogen at -140C until ready for thaw and administration. Keep infusion bag(s) in the metal cassette(s). Once thawed do not re-freeze.

title.value: 10. SPECIAL PRECAUTIONS FOR DISPOSAL OF UNUSED MEDICINAL PRODUCTS OR WASTE MATERIALS DERIVED FROM SUCH MEDICINAL PRODUCTS, IF APPROPRIATE

p.span: This medicine contains geneticallymodified cells. Unused medicine must be disposed of in compliance with the local guidelines on handling human-derived material.
